SimplePathXna is a lightweight developemnt framework that wraps XNA 4.0. 

It provides:
 - Command based input detection system
 - Spritesheet animation sub-system
 - State management architecture 

See http://simplepathstudios.com/blog/2011/04/18/new-development-framework-simplepathxna/ for more information on using the template (if using the out of date template system.)

This framework uses the MIT license. See the included license for terms of that license.